    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to level 1 per MRL 2 requirements and confirmed not-assessed with documented justification. Grid convergence index of 2.8% and output comparison deviations below 12% across all operating points provide sufficient confidence that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) is supported by the validation evidence. Assessment accepted.",
